<b>Iain Robertson</b> (born <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../624/19624.xml">
27 May</link> <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../776/34776.xml">
1981</link>) is a <country wordnetid="108544813" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../994/26994.xml">
Scottish</link></country>
 <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../753/753.xml">
actor</link>. <p>

After winning a scholarship to the <school wordnetid="108276720" confidence="0.8">
<educational_institution wordnetid="108276342" confidence="0.8">
<institution wordnetid="108053576" confidence="0.8">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../317/2340317.xml">
Sylvia Young Theatre School</link></institution>
</educational_institution>
</school>
 at the age of 12, he quickly went to work appearing in what are now regarded as classic dramas such as <it><link>
Kavanagh Q.C</link></it>, <it>Silent Witness</it> and <it><statement wordnetid="106722453" confidence="0.8">
<message wordnetid="106598915" confidence="0.8">
<announcement wordnetid="106746580" confidence="0.8">
