</it> for example.  <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../783/2499783.xml">
Gillies Mackinnon</link> wasted no time in casting him as the lead in the feature film <movie wordnetid="106613686" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../127/1430127.xml">
Small Faces (film)</link></movie>
 alongside <actor wordnetid="109765278" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../292/19081292.xml">
Kevin McKidd</link></actor>
, <actor wordnetid="109765278" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../922/867922.xml">
Laura Fraser</link></actor>
 and <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../138/13769138.xml">
Claire Higgins</link> which received world wide critical success and earned Iain a <it>Best Performance <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../943/147943.xml">
BAFTA</link></it></p>
